    title: 'Aluminium Windows for Tenement Flats in Edinburgh: What You Need to Know',
    excerpt: 'Tenement flats present unique challenges for window replacement. Here is how aluminium windows can solve noise, security, and thermal problems in Edinburgh\'s iconic sandstone buildings.',
    date: 'April 2, 2026',
    author: 'Lead Engineer',
